message: Can you please give me names of companies that are doing data warehousing, BI and analytics in Egypt?

data.message: فى حد كنت اعرفو كان شغال فى اوركال فى البيزنس انتلجنس

EMC², Teradata, Orange and Oracle are some of the ones I can think of now.
Edit: Well you got Siemens too, they offer some big data solutions for healthcare industries but I don't know if that's operational in Egypt. IBM as well as Microsoft. Also Orange is just a shot in the dark.
